reviewText: was missing 1 of the movies and couldn't pass up to get complete set for great price.
Fast shipping.  This movie took me back in my years.  So funny.  I laughed and laughed.

These three movies are great when you just want to veg. You don't have to figure anything out or use your brain at all, really. The only thing I DIDN'T like, and it's a big one for me, is that it's in full frame. I know they shot in widescreen. Again, it's kind of an irritation when the seller doesn't reveal what screen format their movies are in. I wish there was a way to force them to do that.
